parameters:
It was quite fun. There were so many things I
didn't know about magic.

There are limits to self-study, you know. Magic
textbooks aren't sold in regular stores either.

Ah, but just studying in a classroom all the time
is boring.

Today is just a coincidence. There are also
classes where we use magic, so don't worry.

I'm looking forward to seeing both of your
abilities from now on.

But I've been alone until now, so I'm happy to
have a roommate.
Ah... I'm starting to feel sleepy.

There's still a little time before bedtime, but if
I go to sleep now...

You must be nervous and tired because it's the
first day.

Um... there's a rule that I haven't told you
yet...
Is it something difficult to say?

Well... I guess... but it's an important rule, so
I have to tell you...

Normally, it's something that seniors tell you
when you move into the dormitory...

(Are there any strict rules that are difficult to
say...)

(I thought about what you were going to say, but
it's definitely an unavoidable issue in communal
living.)

U-um... if you feel like doing it, you're supposed
to tell your roommate.

And the person who is told that has to leave the
room for a while.

So... Masamune-kun, if you feel like doing it,
don't hesitate to tell me!

But... there shouldn't be anything that absolutely
has to be done in the room, right?

Even between men, it's embarrassing to say
something like that.

When it comes to the bath or toilet, um... there's
a possibility of things getting clogged.

Because there aren't many toilets, if you stay in
there for a long time, there might be people who
want to use it but can't...
You don't have to hold back, okay?

(If it wasn't Tommy, I could have said it more
casually...)
(I know they're a guy, but they're cute!)
Tommy, you can say it too.

It's the same Skeleton Head from our class. If
there are new students, we should throw a welcome
party.

He has been wearing this mask since he entered
school. He's just an eccentric person, not a bad
guy.

Well then, let's raise a toast to celebrate that
we're in the same Howard Dormitory!
I haven't even prepared any drinks yet...
First, let's go to class once we're ready.
